==English==

'''User Friendly Definition:'''
A species of plant or animal that has died out completely.

'''Examples:'''
Carolina parakeet, passenger pigeon, dodo bird
 
'''Tennessee Grade Level and Content Area:'''
3 - Earth and Space Science

'''Tennessee Curriculum Framework Connection:'''


'''Embedded Learning Context:''' 
Aniamls can become extinct if the places where they live change too much for them to adapt. 

'''Derived Terms'''
extinction: occurs when living examples of a plant or animal no longer exist.

